nd then after a lot of hard work we finally got funds for new farm buildings.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-3-test-1-part-3-2023-08-14-20-27-20/51.mp3","time_start":136.09,"time_end":140.82},{"position":52,"content":"And you wanted to see things through?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-3-test-1-part-3-2023-08-14-20-27-20/52.mp3","time_start":140.82,"time_end":143.33},{"position":53,"content":"And that's why you want to train to teach Geography?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-3-test-1-part-3-2023-08-14-20-27-20/53.mp3","time_start":143.33,"time_end":146.1},{"position":54,"content":"Yes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-3-test-1-part-3-2023-08-14-20-27-20/54.mp3","time_start":146.1,"time_end":147.08},{"position":55,"content":"I've had a couple of jobs since then","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-3-test-1-part-3-2023-08-14-20-27-20/55.mp3","time_start":147.47,"time_end":149.59},{"position":56,"content":"but I now realise I like teaching best.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-3-test-1-part-3-2023-08-14-20-27-20/56.mp3","time_start":149.85,"time_end":152.6},{"position":57,"content":"And I chose Geography because...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-3-test-1-part-3-2023-08-14-20-27-20/57.mp3","time_start":152.9,"time_end":155.2},{"position":58,"content":"because it is my favourite subject...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-3-test-1-part-3-2023-08-14-20-27-20/58.mp3","time_start":155.72,"time_end":157.69},{"position":59,"content":"and also because I think it has so many useful applications.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-3-test-1-part-3-2023-08-14-20-